Creates a Config with the specified configData parameters

Source: R/groundstation_operations.R
groundstation_create_config.Rd

Creates a Config with the specified configData parameters.

Only one type of configData can be specified.

groundstation_create_config(configData, name, tags)

Arguments

configData

[required] Parameters of a Config.
name

[required] Name of a Config.
tags

Tags assigned to a Config.

Request syntax

svc$create_config(
  configData = list(
    antennaDownlinkConfig = list(
      spectrumConfig = list(
        bandwidth = list(
          units = "GHz"|"MHz"|"kHz",
          value = 123.0
        ),
        centerFrequency = list(
          units = "GHz"|"MHz"|"kHz",
          value = 123.0
        ),
        polarization = "LEFT_HAND"|"NONE"|"RIGHT_HAND"
      )
    ),
    antennaDownlinkDemodDecodeConfig = list(
      decodeConfig = list(
        unvalidatedJSON = "string"
      ),
      demodulationConfig = list(
        unvalidatedJSON = "string"
      ),
      spectrumConfig = list(
        bandwidth = list(
          units = "GHz"|"MHz"|"kHz",
          value = 123.0
        ),
        centerFrequency = list(
          units = "GHz"|"MHz"|"kHz",
          value = 123.0
        ),
        polarization = "LEFT_HAND"|"NONE"|"RIGHT_HAND"
      )
    ),
    antennaUplinkConfig = list(
      spectrumConfig = list(
        centerFrequency = list(
          units = "GHz"|"MHz"|"kHz",
          value = 123.0
        ),
        polarization = "LEFT_HAND"|"NONE"|"RIGHT_HAND"
      ),
      targetEirp = list(
        units = "dBW",
        value = 123.0
      ),
      transmitDisabled = TRUE|FALSE
    ),
    dataflowEndpointConfig = list(
      dataflowEndpointName = "string",
      dataflowEndpointRegion = "string"
    ),
    trackingConfig = list(
      autotrack = "PREFERRED"|"REMOVED"|"REQUIRED"
    ),
    uplinkEchoConfig = list(
      antennaUplinkConfigArn = "string",
      enabled = TRUE|FALSE
    )
  ),
  name = "string",
  tags = list(
    "string"
  )
)
